Status.name: Building
Status.description: Source code has been committed, and JIRA is waiting for the code to be built before moving to the next status.

Status.name: Open
Status.description: The work item is open and ready for the assignee to start work on it.

Status.name: In Progress
Status.description: This work item is being actively worked on at the moment by the assignee.

Status.name: Reopened
Status.description: This work item was once resolved, but the resolution was deemed incorrect. From here the work items are either reopened, or are closed.

Status.name: Resolved
Status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it's awaiting verification by the reporter. From here work items are either reopened, or are closed.

Status.name: Closed
Status.description: The work item is considered finished, the resolution is correct. work items which are closed can be reopened.

Status.name: Build Broken
Status.description: The source code committed for this work item has possibly broken the build.
